        Level-2 Opponent's Attack: {"claim": "The opposition misunderstands the role and impact of modern teachers unions, painting them as uniformly obstructive, which is untrue.", "argument": ["The opposition overgeneralizes the impact of teachers unions.", "The claim that all unions obstruct school improvement is false."]}
